second cut
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:2
Definition:a lock of wool missed by a shearer and subsequently shorn.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
